quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,"“Ndikulumbira (angelo) amene amandanda m’mizere yondondozana, (popembedza ndi kugonjera Mbuye wawo)"
  37,2,“Ndi omwe amaletsa zoipa
  37,3,“Ndi omwe amalalika ulaliki (wa Allah ndi kumtamanda mochulukira)
  37,4,“Ndithu Mulungu wanu ndi mmodzi basi
  37,5,"“Mbuye wathambo ndi nthaka, ndi zapakati pake; ndiponso Mbuye wa kuvuma konse"
  37,6,“Ndithu tidalikongoletsa thambo lapafupi (ndi inu) ndi chokongoletsa cha nyenyezi (zowala)
  37,7,“Ndi kuti lisungidwe ku satana aliyense wogalukira (lamulo la Allah)
  37,8,“Kuti asamvere (zomwe zikunenedwa ndi) gulu lolemekezeka (la angelo). Ndipo akugendedwa (ndi kupirikitsidwa) mbali zonse
  37,9,“Kuthamangitsidwa mwamphamvu; ndipo chilango chonkerankera patsogolo chili pa iwo
  37,10,"“Kupatula amene wazembetsa mawu (akumwamba), ndipo chikumtsatira iye chenje cha moto chowala kwambiri"
  37,11,"“Tawafunsa (otsutsa zouka ku imfa): “Kodi iwo ngovuta kuwalenga kuposa zimene tidalenga, (monga: thambo, nthaka, nyenyezi ndi zina zotere)?” Ndithu Ife tidawalenga kuchokera ku dongo lonyata"
  37,12,"“Koma iwe (Mneneri) ukudabwa (za kutsutsa kwawo kuuka ku imfa pomwe zisonyezo zilipo zambirimbiri), ndipo akukuchitira chipongwe (kudabwa kwako)"
  37,13,"“Ndipo akalalikiridwa, salalikirika"
  37,14,"“Ndipo akachiona chisonyezo (chosonyeza kukhoza kwa Allah,) amachichitira chipongwe"
  37,15,"“Ndipo osakhulupirira amanena: “Palibe chilipo apa, koma ndi matsenga woonekera poyera.”"
  37,16,"““Kodi tikadzafa ndi kusanduka fumbi ndi mafupa, tidzatulutsidwanso (kuchokera m’manda tili amoyo)?”"
  37,17,““Pamodzi ndi makolo athu akale?”
  37,18,"“Nena (iwe Mneneri): “Inde (mudzaukitsidwa inu pamodzi ndi makolo anu) uku inu muli onyozeka.”"
  37,19,"“Ndithu (kuukako) ndimkuwe umodzi adzangodzidzimuka ali moyo, akuyang’ana"
  37,20,"“Ndipo adzanena (okanawo): “Kalanga ife! Kuonongeka nkwathu! Ili nditsiku lija lamalipiro!”"
  37,21,"“(Adzawauza): “Ili nditsiku la chiweruziro lomwe mumalitsutsa lija.”"
  37,22,"“(Kudzanenedwa kwa angelo): “Asonkhanitseni amene adali osalungama pamodzi ndi akazi awo (okana Allah) ndi milungu yawo imene amaipembedza,”"
  37,23,"““Kusiya Allah, ndipo asonyezeni njira ya ku Jahannam.”"
  37,24,"““Koma aimikeni pano chifukwa iwo afunsidwa (za chikhulupiliro chawo ndi zochita zawo):”"
  37,25,““Kodi nchifukwa ninji inu (opembedza mafano) simukupulumutsana (monga mumanenera pa dziko lapansi kuti mudzapulumutsana)?”
  37,26,“Koma iwo pa tsikulo adzagonjera ndi kudzipereka (ku lamulo la Allah)
  37,27,“Ndipo adzatembenukirana ndi kuyamba kufunsana (ndi kudzudzulana)
  37,28,"“Ndipo (ofooka) adzanena (kwa odzikweza): “Inu mumatidzera kumbali komwe timakuganizira kuti nkwabwino (ndi kutichotsako kunka nafe ku njira yopotoka)"
  37,29,"“(Odzikweza) adzayankha: “Koma simudali okhulupirira.”"
  37,30,"““Ndipo tidalibe nyonga zokuponderezerani inu, koma mudali anthu opyola malire (ndi kutuluka ku choonadi cha Allah).”"
  37,31,““Choncho mawu a Mbuye wathu (onena za chilango) atsimikizika pa ife; ndithu ife tichilawa (chilango).”
  37,32,““Tidakusokeretsani; nafenso tidali osokera. (Choncho musatidzudzule).”
  37,33,“Ndithu iwo akathandizana chilango tsiku limenelo (la chiweruziro)
  37,34,“Ndithu (chilango chonga chimenecho) ndimomwe timawachitira olakwira (Allah)
  37,35,“Ndithu iwo ankati akauzidwa kuti palibe wopembedzedwa mwa choonadi koma Allah ankadzitukumula
  37,36,"“Ndipo ankanena: “Kodi ife tisiye kupembedza milungu yathu chifukwa cha zonena za mlakatuli, wopenga?”"
  37,37,“Iyayi koma adawadzera ndi choonadi (Mthenga wawo Muhammad yemwe siwamisala kapena wolakatula zopeka) ndipo adawatsimikizira za atumiki
  37,38,“Ndithu inu (osakhulupirira) mudzalawa chilango chowawa
  37,39,“Ndipo simudzalipidwa kupatula zokhazo zimene mumachita
  37,40,“Kupatula akapolo a Allah oyeretsedwa
  37,41,“Kwa iwo kuli zopatsidwa zodziwika (ndi Mbuye wawo Allah)
  37,42,“Zipatso (zamtundu uliwonse); ndipo iwo adzalandira ulemu (waukulu)
  37,43,“M’minda ya mtendere
  37,44,“Adzakhala pa makama (a mtengo wapatali) uku akuyang’anizana
  37,45,“Uku zikuwazungulira zikho zodzazidwa ndi zakumwa zochokera m’kasupe woyenda nthawi zonse
  37,46,"“Woyera, wokoma kwa akumwa (zakumwazo)"
  37,47,“(M’zakumwazo) mulibe zopweteketsa mutu (kwa ozimwa) ndiponso iwo sadzaledzera nazo
  37,48,"“Ndipo kwa iwo kudzakhala akazi oyang’ana iwo okha, ophanuka maso (okongola)"
  37,49,“Onga ngati dzira (la nthiwatiwa) losungidwa (m’mapiko)
  37,50,“Ndipo adzayang’anizana ndi kuyamba kufunsana (pakati pawo)
  37,51,"“Adzanena wonena mmodzi wa iwo: “Ine ndidali ndi mnzanga (wopembedza mafano amene amatsutsana nane za chipembedzo ndi zophunzitsa za Qur’an yolemekezeka).”"
  37,52,"“Yemwe amandiuza: “Kodi iwe ndiwe mmodzi wa ovomereza?”"
  37,53,"““Zakuti tikadzafa ndi kusanduka fumbi ndi mafupa, (tidzaukanso) ndi kulandira malipiro (pa zochita zathu)?”"
  37,54,"“(Wokhulupirira) adzanena (kwa anzake: “Inu anthu a kumtendere) kodi simungasuzumire (nane ku moto kuti timuone)?”"
  37,55,“Choncho adzayang’ana ndipo adzamuona ali mkatikati mwa moto
  37,56,"“Adzanena: “Ndikulumbilira Allah! Udatsala pang’ono kuti undiononge (ndikadakuvomera paja pa dziko lapansi).”"
  37,57,"““Ndipo pakadapanda chisomo cha Mbuye wanga, ndikadakhala mmodzi mwa opezeka ku Moto.”"
  37,58,““Kodi zili choncho kuti sitidzafanso (tizingosangalala m’Munda wamtendere).”
  37,59,"““Kupatula imfa yathu yoyamba ija, ndi kutinso ife sitilangidwa?”"
  37,60,“Ndithu izi (zimene Allah waika m’Munda wamtendere) ndiko kupambana kwakukulu
  37,61,“(Pofuna kupeza) zonga zimenezi ogwira ntchito agwire
  37,62,“Kodi zimenezo ndilo phwando labwino kapena mtengo wa Zaqqum (wowawa kwambiri womwe anthu a ku Moto azikadya)
  37,63,“Ndithu Ife taupanga (mtengo umenewu) kukhala mayeso ndi chilango cha anthu ochimwa (podzichitira okha chinyengo ndi kupembedza mafano)
  37,64,“Umenewu ndimtengo omwe umatuluka pakatikati pa Jahannam (adaulenga kuchokera ku Moto)
  37,65,“Zipatso zake (nzoipa) ngati mitu ya asatana
  37,66,“Ndithu iwo akadya mtengowo ndi kudzaza mimba zawo ndi zipatso zake (pakuti sakapeza chakudya china kupatula zipatso za mtengowo)
  37,67,"“Kenako, ndithu kuwawa kwa mtengowo kosakanikirana ndi madzi owira kuzakhala pa iwo"
  37,68,“Kenako ndithu kobwerera kwawo ndi ku Jahannam
  37,69,“Ndithu iwo adapeza makolo awo ali osokera
  37,70,“Ndipo iwonso adatsata mapazi awo mothamanga
  37,71,"“Ndipo, ndithu akale ambiri adasokera patsogolo pawo"
  37,72,"“Ndipo, ndithu tidatuma achenjezi kwa iwo"
  37,73,“Tapenya momwe adalili mapeto a omwe adachenjezedwa
  37,74,"“Kupatula akapolo a Allah, oyeretsedwa (iwo ndiwo anthu a ku Munda wamtendere)"
  37,75,"“Ndithu Nuh adatiitana, (ndipo tidamuyankha mayankho abwino), taonani kukhala bwino Ife Oyankha"
  37,76,“Ndipo tidampulumutsa iye ndi anthu ake ku vuto lalikulu
  37,77,"“Ndipo tidazichita zidzukulu zake kukhala zotsala (pa dziko, oipa ataonongeka)"
  37,78,“Ndipo tidamsiira mbiri yabwino kwa mibadwo yodza pambuyo pake
  37,79,“Mtendere ukhale pa Nuh pa zolengedwa zonse
  37,80,“Ndithu umu ndimomwe Ife tilipirira ochita zabwino
  37,81,“Ndithu iye ndi mmodzi mwa akapolo Athu okhulupirira
  37,82,“Kenako tidawamiza enawo
  37,83,“Ndipo ndithu m’gulu lake (la Nuh) muli Ibrahim
  37,84,“Kumbuka pamene adadza kwa Mbuye wake ndi mtima wabwino (wogonjera malamulo)
  37,85,"“Pomwe adanena kwa bambo wake ndi anthu ake: “Mukupembedza chiyani?”"
  37,86,"““Ha! Milungu yopeka kusiya Allah, ndi imene mukuifuna?”"
  37,87,““Kodi maganizo anu ngotani pa Mbuye wa zolengedwa zonse?”
  37,88,“Ndipo adayang’ana nyenyezi mozama
  37,89,"“Ndipo adanena: “Ine ndine wodwala!”"
  37,90,“Choncho iwo adatembenuka ndi kumsiya
  37,91,"“(Ibrahim) adapita mozemba ku mafano awo, ndipo adawauza (mwachipongwe:) “Bwanji simukudya (chakudya chomwe chaikidwa patsogolo panupo)?”"
  37,92,““Bwanji simukuyankhula?”
  37,93,“Atatero adawatembenukira ndi kuwamenya (mwamphamvu) ndi dzanja lamanja
  37,94,“(Pamene adamva eni mafanowo) adadza kwa iye akuthamanga
  37,95,"“Anati: “Kodi mukupembedza (miyala) imene mwasema?”"
  37,96,““Chikhalirecho Allah ndiye adakulengani ndi zimene mukuchita!”
  37,97,"“Iwo adati: “Mmangireni ng’anjo, ndipo mponyeni m’motowo.”"
  37,98,"“Adafuna kumchita chiwembu (kuti amuphe ndi moto), koma tidawachita kukhala onyozeka"
  37,99,"“Ndipo (Ibrahim) adati: “Ndithu ine ndikupita kwa Mbuye wanga, Iye andiongolera.”"
  37,100,““E Mbuye wanga! Ndipatseni mwana yemwe adzakhale (mmodzi) mwa olungama!”
  37,101,"“Ndipo tidamuuza nkhani yabwino ya mwana wofatsa, (mwanayo ndi Ismaila)"
  37,102,"“Ndipo (adabadwa ndi kuyamba kukula.) Pamene adakwana nsinkhu woyenda pamodzi ndi tate wake pochitachita za m’dziko (Ibrahim adayesedwa mayeso kupyolera m’maloto omwe adalota). Adati: “E mwana wanga! Ine kutulo ndikuona maloto (owona ochokera kwa Allah omwe akundilamula) kuti ndikuzinge (monga nsembe yopereka kwa Allah). Nanga ukuti bwanji?” (Mwana wabwino) adanena: “Bambo wanga! Kwaniritsani chimene mukulamulidwa. Ngati Allah afuna, mundipeza ndili mmodzi mwa opirira.”"
  37,103,"“Pamene adagonjera onse awiri (chofuna cha Allah), ndipo (Ibrahim) adam’goneka chakumphumi (ndipo adatsimikiza kumupha)"
  37,104,"“Ndipo tidamuitana: “E iwe Ibrahim!”"
  37,105,““Ndithu wavomereza maloto! (Choncho usamuphe mwana wakoyo).” Umo ndi momwe timawalipirira ochita zabwino
  37,106,“Ndithu amenewa ndimayeso oonekera
  37,107,“Ndipo tidampulumutsa pompatsa nyama yayikulu (yoti apereke nsembe)
  37,108,“Ndipo tidamsiira (mbiri yabwino) kwa anthu ena (amene adadza pambuyo pake)
  37,109,“Mtendere ukhale pa Ibrahim
  37,110,“M’menemo ndi mornwe timawalipirira ochita zabwino
  37,111,“Ndithu iye adali mmodzi mwa akapolo Athu okhulupirira
  37,112,“Ndiponso tidamuuza nkhani yabwino (yoti akhala ndi mwana wotchedwa) Isihaqa; mneneri; wam’gulu la olungama
  37,113,“Ndipo tidamdalitsa iye ndi (mwana wake) Isihaqa; ndipo m’mbumba ya awiriwa mudapezeka abwino ndi odzichitira zoipa owonekera
  37,114,"“Ndipo ndithu tidawachitira zabwino Mûsa ndi Haruna, (powapatsa uneneri ndi madalitso ambiri)"
  37,115,“Ndipo tidawapulumutsa (awiriwa) ndi anthu awo ku vuto lalikulu
  37,116,"“Ndipo tidawathangata (powagonjetsera adani awo), ndipo iwo adali opambana"
  37,117,“Ndipo tidawapatsa (Mûsa ndi Haruna) buku losonyeza poyera (malamulo)
  37,118,“Ndipo tidawaongolera ku njira yolunjika
  37,119,“Ndiponso tidawasiira (mbiri yabwino) kwa anthu ena (amene adadza pambuyo pawo)
  37,120,“Mtendere ukhale pa Mûsa ndi Haruna
  37,121,“Ndithu umu ndi momwe Ife timawalipirira ochita zabwino
  37,122,“Ndithu awiriwa adali m’gulu la akapoio Athu okhulupirira
  37,123,“Ndipo ndithu Iliyasa ndi mmodzi wa atumiki
  37,124,"“(Kumbuka) pamene adanena kwa anthu ake: “Bwanji simuopa (Allah)?”"
  37,125,““Mukupembedza (fano lotchedwa) Ba’la ndi kusiya (kupembedza) Wabwino zedi mwa olenga onse.”
  37,126,"““Allah, Mbuye wanu ndi Mbuye wa makolo anu akale?”"
  37,127,“Koma adamtsutsa; ndithu iwo adzaonekera (ku Moto)
  37,128,“Kupatula akapolo a Allah amene ayeretsedwa (ndi Allah)
  37,129,“Ndipo tidamsiira (mbiri yabwino) kwa anthu ena (amene adadza pambuyo pake)
  37,130,“Mtendere ukhale pa Iliyasiin
  37,131,“Ndithu umo ndi mmene Ife timawalipirira ochita zabwino
  37,132,“Ndithu iye ndimmodzi mwa akapolo Athu okhulupirira
  37,133,“Ndithu Luti ndi mmodzi wa atumiki
  37,134,“(Kumbuka) pamene tidampulumutsa iye ndi anthu ake onse
  37,135,“Kupatula nkhalamba yachikazi; idali mwa otsalira
  37,136,“Kenako tidawaononga enawo (omwe adali oipa)
  37,137,“Ndithu inu (a mumzinda wa Makka) mumadutsa pa malo pawopo m’mawa
  37,138,“Ndi usiku. Kodi bwanji simuzindikira
  37,139,“Ndithu Yunusu ndi mmodzi wa atumiki
  37,140,“(Kumbuka) pamene adathawira m’chombo chodzazidwa (ndi katundu)
  37,141,"“Choncho adachita mayere, ndipo adali m’gulu la omgwera (mayerewo)"
  37,142,“Choncho nsomba idammeza uku ali wodzudzulidwa
  37,143,“Kukadapanda kuti iye adali m’modzi mwa otamanda ndi kulemekeza Allah
  37,144,“Akadakhala m’mimba mwake mpaka tsiku loukitsidwa (zolengedwa ku imfa)
  37,145,“Koma tidamponya pa gombe uku ali wodwala
  37,146,“Ndipo tidammeretsera mmera wa mtundu wa nkhaka
  37,147,"“Ndipo (atachira) tidamtuma ku anthu okwana zikwi zana limodzi (,000) kapena kupambana apa"
  37,148,“Ndipo adakhulupirira (ndi kuvomereza ulaliki wake); choncho tidawapatsa chisangalalo kufikira nthawi (ya imfa yawo)
  37,149,"“Choncho afunse: “Kodi Mbuye wako ndiye woyenera ana aakazi, ndipo iwo aamuna? (Pomwe iwo akabereka mwana wamkazi amanyansidwa naye)!”"
  37,150,"“Kapena kuti tidalenga angelo kukhala akazi, iwo akuona"
  37,151,"“Chenjera ndi bodza lawolo, ndithu iwo akunena"
  37,152,““Allah wabereka.” Ndithu iwo ndi abodza
  37,153,“Kodi Iye adasankha ana aakazi kusiya aamuna
  37,154,“Kodi nchiyani chakupezani (kuti muweruze mopanda chilungamo); nanga mukuweruza bwanji (zimenezi)
  37,155,"“Kodi bwanji simukumbukira, (mwaiwala zisonyezo Zake zodabwitsa ndi kupatukana kwake ndi zimenezo)"
  37,156,“Kapena inu muli ndi umboni woonekera (wochokera kumwamba)
  37,157,“Tabweretsani buku lanulo (momwe mwalembedwa zimenezi) ngati mukunena zoona
  37,158,“Ndipo adapeka chibale pakati pa Iye (Allah) ndi ziwanda; (pomwe ziwanda nzobisika kwa iwo). Ndithu ziwanda zimadziwa kuti iwo osakhulupirira akaonekera (kwa Allah kuti aweruzidwe)
  37,159,“Walemekezeka Allah! Ndi kupatukana ndi zimene akumnamizira
  37,160,“Koma akapolo a Allah oyeretsedwa (ali kutali ndi zimene akusimba osakhulupirirazi)
  37,161,“Ndithu inu (osakhulupirira) ndi zimene mukuzipembedza (kusiya Allah)
  37,162,“Ndi zimenezo simungamsokeretse aliyense
  37,163,“Kupatula yemwe (Allah adadziwa kuti) ngolowa ku Jahannam
  37,164,"“Ndipo (angelo adanena): “Aliyense mwa ife ali ndi malo ake odziwika.”"
  37,165,““Ndipo ndithu (ena mwa) ife ngondanda m’mizere (ya mapemphero nthawi zonse).”
  37,166,““Ndipo (ena mwa) ife ngolemekeza (Allah nthawi zonse ndi kumtamanda ndi kumpatula ku zinthu zosayenerana ndi ulemelero wake).”
  37,167,“Ndipo (osakhulupirira) ankati
  37,168,““Tikadakhala ndi buku monga lomwe anthu akale adali nalo.”
  37,169,"““Tikadakhala akapolo a Allah, oyeretsedwa.”"
  37,170,"“Koma (pamene lidawadzera bukulo), adalikana; choncho posachedwa adziwa (zotsatira zake)"
  37,171,“Ndipo ndithu liwu lathu lidatsogola kwa akapolo athu otumidwa
  37,172,“(Kuti) ndithu iwo ngopulumutsidwa
  37,173,“Ndipo ndithu asilikali Athu ndi opambana
  37,174,"“Choncho, asiye kwa kanthawi kochepa"
  37,175,“Ndipo ingowayang’ana basi; posachedwapa aona
  37,176,“Kodi chilango chathu akuchifulumizitsa
  37,177,"“Choncho chikadzatsika pabwalo lawo, udzakhala mmawa woipa kwa ochenjezedwa"
  37,178,“Ndipo asiye kwa kanthawi kochepa
  37,179,“Ndipo ingowayang’ana basi; posachedwapa aona
  37,180,"“Mbuye wako, Mwini ulemelero, wapatukana ndi zimene akumnamizira (osakhulupirira)"
  37,181,“Ndipo mtendere ukhale pa atumiki onse
  37,182,"“Ndipo kuyamikidwa konse nkwa Allah, Mbuye wa zolengedwa zonse"